snippet.title: Birthdays the Beginning - TGS Trailer (PS4, Steam)
snippet.description:
Official Website: BirthdaystheBeginning.com
Check out the Limited Edition at http://store.nisamerica.com/birthdays-the-beginning-limited-edition

From legendary creator Mr. Yasuhiro Wada, comes Birthdays the Beginning, a new sandbox game in which players create cube-shaped worlds that give rise to diverse and unique lifeforms. With careful experimentation, players can shape the geography and alter the temperature of their world to create the conditions for life and witness the birth of an entire ecosystem!
